title: Winning Back His Wife  by A.B. Ewing
description:
When Caleb Seth Wilder rescues a child from
a wrecked car on his way home from work, he is
devastated to find that the near dead driver is his
estranged wife and that the child he saves is his.

After Neela wakes from her accident, it is only to find
that she is paralyzed. She may be able to walk again,
but it will take time and money. Money that she doesn't
have, but her husband does.Caleb will help her,but
accepting his help comes with a price. She has to move
back home, but going back will mean facing the past
and the person responsible for her leaving.
